[In a report from 29 Oct 2015 http://abc7news.com/health/worker-tests-positive-for-shigella-at-restaurant-linked-to-200-cases/1058184/, a restaurant employee was also found have shigellosis but is felt to be a part of the outbreak, not the cause of it. - Mod.LL

